{"tid":1187324,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"好多","createTime":"2019-06-05T14:34:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-05T16:57:53.000Z","uid":238801,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"76cc0d76681054b627fe9cefce9ded3ca20da153","tid":1187324,"uid":238801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T14:34:27.000Z","msg":"值得諗<br />\n本有句值得諗 好有意思<br />\n愛情係一種將自己所有武器放低嘅慾望<br />\n個問題係 我驚打擊驚到唔想再<br />\n就算小王子比到啲安慰我<br />\n話我知重要嘅係小麥的顏色<br />\n但呢樣嘢本來就好奇怪<br />\n我甚至唔知自己點解需要佢 點解佢會出現<br />\n點解人要咁反反覆覆咁投入喺呢樣嘢入面<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />利申仲係未睇曬 睇得慢兼3分鐘<br />\n繼續睇先"},{"pid":"965511e65cf127009577ffa27e8dcd79b98d9949","tid":1187324,"uid":238801,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T14:34:59.000Z","msg":"一半都未完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔好理我住"},{"pid":"1680b13cf59e1ea47978c06123562a284171e2e3","tid":1187324,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"965511e65cf127009577ffa27e8dcd79b98d9949","tid":1187324,"uid":238801,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T14:34:59.000Z","msg":"一半都未完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔好理我住"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T14:40:33.000Z","msg":"好啦👌"},{"pid":"037206f8ef11d9e954d5c40d619ec5344e5b831c","tid":1187324,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"965511e65cf127009577ffa27e8dcd79b98d9949","tid":1187324,"uid":238801,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T14:34:59.000Z","msg":"一半都未完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔好理我住"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T14:42:25.000Z","msg":"冇問題"},{"pid":"597062792e5377b85a47f95a4d987b03f1553e0f","tid":1187324,"uid":124256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T15:39:17.000Z","msg":"樓煮咁有心機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good